# One pattern per line. Use for one-off exclusions that don't fit
# lychee.toml's regex `exclude` list (e.g., a single flaky vendor URL).
#
# Add an explanation comment above each entry so the next reviewer
# knows why it's here.

# windsorcli.github.io is the website repo; not public yet, so the
# URL 404s from GitHub's public API. Remove this once the repo is
# published.
^https://github\.com/windsorcli/windsorcli\.github\.io

# Intel support PDFs (content/dam) return 403 to automated clients; valid in a browser.
^https://www\.intel\.com/content/dam/support/.+\.pdf$
